snippet.title: Interns of Ecstasy Island - Player Character Avatar Clothing Test
snippet.description:
A quick test of the body variations for the player character for Interns of Ecstasy Island. New hair variations were added as well as all current clothing options.

More details on the game are available on my blog.
https://usagitriplesix.home.blog/
